  "title": "Skin Safe White Glue - Daily Wear",
  "body_html": "<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Sunshine Skin Safe Daily Wear Liquid Toupee and Wig Adhesive is an acrylic-based skin-safe liquid adhesive that offers a bond of one to 14 days on lace bases, skin bases, and poly perimeters on lace or monofilament bases. A thinner version of the super-strong Sunshine Skin Safe Extended Wear Liquid Adhesive, it dries clear and offers no-mess cleanup.</span></p>\n<ul data-mce-fragment=\"1\">\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Non-Flammable</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Base: Acrylic\u00a0</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Skin Safe</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Hold:\u00a0Daily Wear\u00a0(1-14 days)</li>\n<li data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Comparable: Walker's Mity-Tite\u00ae</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><small data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Directions:\u00a0</small></span></h2>\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Use as needed for touchups if hair system lifts\u00a0</span><br data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Step 1:\u00a0Apply to skin or base, and blow dry until tacky.\u00a0<br data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Step 2: Press\u00a0hair system to the skin, and hold firmly for 10 seconds.\u00a0</span></p>",
